f=Cybersecurity/CYBERSECURITY-REDESIGN-PLAN-v2.md · h1:Cybersecurity Department Redesign Plan=**Status:** PLAN (for discussion, approved, nothing rebuilt yet) **Supersedes:** CYBERSECURITY-REDESIGN-PLAN.md (v1 DRAFT) **Key change v1:** skill categorized marketplace evidence direct preview URLs. Approximately half previously-"custom" skills viable marketplace alternatives adopted merged. · h2:Agent warden (CISO Security Governance) LEADER=Total skills: Rebuild: kept, swapped, new merge, wrapping model updated. · h3:1.1 security-policy-framework=**Current status:** Custom (wraps Sushegaad GRC pack) **Recommended:** Custom Marketplace (keep wrapping model, switch primary pack) **Marketplace candidates found:** · h3:1.1 security-policy-framework=\| Skill \| Source \| URL \| · h3:1.1 security-policy-framework=\|---\|---\|---\| · h3:1.1 security-policy-framework=\| **GRCEngClub/claude-grc-engineering** (96 skills, RECOMMENDED) \| SkillsMP \| https://skillsmp.com/creators/grcengclub/claude-grc-engineering \| · h3:1.1 security-policy-framework=\| **Hack23/cia** (80 skills — alternative) \| SkillsMP \| https://skillsmp.com/creators/hack23/cia \| · h3:1.1 security-policy-framework=\| **Sushegaad GRC packs** (current — narrower) \| GitHub \| https://github.com/Sushegaad/Claude-Skills-Governance-Risk-and-Compliance \| · h3:1.1 security-policy-framework=GRCEngClub covers: NIST CSF 2.0 expert, ISO 27001, SOC CIS Controls, CMMC v2.0, FedRAMP, PCI DSS, NIST 800-171, APRA CPS 234, MAS TRM, NERC CIP, CCPA/CPRA, Japan APPI, plus GRC diagram builders (audit workflow, control maps, data flow, RACI, risk treatment, shared responsibility). skills total. Hack23/cia covers: ISO 27001 controls, NIST CSF 2.0, CIS v8.1, Cyber Resilience Act, compliance checklists frameworks), classification policy, ISMS compliance, access control policy, data protection. **Decision rationale:** Switch primary Sushegaad GRCEngClub breadth (96 skills vs. per-framework packs). Keep wrapping model marketplace supplies authoritative, maintained control content; warden adds business-specific mapping, ownership, gap-tracking. overlay fleet IP. · h3:1.2 risk-register=**Current status:** Custom (with risk_score.py script, tested) **Recommended:** Merge Anthropic risk-assessment Sentinel Stack risk-register custom risk_score.py **Marketplace candidates found:** · h3:1.2 risk-register=\| Skill \| Source \| URL \| · h3:1.2 risk-register=\|---\|---\|---\| · h3:1.2 risk-register=\| **Anthropic risk-assessment** (19,987 stars) \| SkillsMP \| https://skillsmp.com/skills/anthropics-knowledge-work-plugins-operations-skills-risk-assessment-skill-md \| · h3:1.2 risk-register=\| **Sentinel Stack risk-register** (by aadityaparab) \| SkillsMP \| https://skillsmp.com/es/creators/aadityaparab/sentinel-stack/skills-risk-register \| · h3:1.2 risk-register=\| **Existing custom risk_score.py** \| Already built \| `/scripts/risk_score.py` \| · h3:1.2 risk-register=Anthropic risk-assessment OFFICIAL Anthropic skill 19,987 stars. Covers risk categories (Operational, Financial, Compliance, Strategic, Reputational, Security) Low/Medium/High matrix prioritized risk register output. Sentinel Stack risk-register living register auto-populates guardrail detections, uses 5×5 likelihood-impact matrix, tracks treatment plans (accept/mitigate/transfer/avoid), generates leadership reports, covers Data Privacy, Ethics, Regulatory, Operational, Reputational, Financial categories. **Decision rationale:** Merge. Anthropic methodology (20K-validated star rating), Sentinel Stack auto-population reporting, risk_score.py deterministic arithmetic input data available. "acceptance routes board" discipline stays custom overlay. · h3:1.3 third-party-risk=**Current status:** Custom (with vendor-assessment-template.md) **Recommended:** Marketplace Anthropic vendor-review vendor-ai-risk **Marketplace candidates found:** · h3:1.3 third-party-risk=\| Skill \| Source \| URL \| · h3:1.3 third-party-risk=\|---\|---\|---\| · h3:1.3 third-party-risk=\| **Anthropic vendor-review** (OFFICIAL Anthropic) \| SkillsMP \| https://skillsmp.com/skills/anthropics-knowledge-work-plugins-operations-skills-vendor-review-skill-md \| · h3:1.3 third-party-risk=\| **vendor-ai-risk** (by aadityaparab) \| SkillsMP \| https://skillsmp.com/pt/creators/aadityaparab/sentinel-stack/skills-vendor-ai-risk \| · h3:1.3 third-party-risk=\| **vendor-management** (by alirezarezvani) \| SkillsMP \| https://skillsmp.com/es/skills/alirezarezvani-claude-skills-business-operations-skills-vendor-management-skill-md \| · h3:1.3 third-party-risk=Anthropic vendor-review OFFICIAL Anthropic skill. Structured evaluation: cost analysis (TCO including implementation, migration, exit costs), risk assessment (financial stability, security/compliance, concentration risk, contract lock-in), performance metrics (SLA compliance, support response, uptime), comparison matrix. Output: Proceed Negotiate Pass recommendation. vendor-ai-risk adds specialized 5-dimension vendor assessment (security, privacy, AI-specific risks, contractual, regulatory) Quick Triage min) Deep Due Diligence modes. 0-100 scorecard dimension. **Decision rationale:** Anthropic official skill exactly what custom version does, better, 18+ month maintenance track record. Add vendor-ai-risk specifically vendor assessments (growing category custom skill doesn't address). · h3:1.4 security-exception-process=**Current status:** Custom (with exception-register-template.md) **Recommended:** Custom (keep as-is) **Marketplace candidates found:** None. Searched skillsmp.com, mcpmarket.com, awesomeskill.ai standalone exception-process security-waiver agent skill exists. **Decision rationale:** Genuine marketplace gap. time-boxed, compensating-controlled, fail-closed expiry workflow fleet-specific derived edge/scout's gate discipline. Keep as-is. · h2:Agent bastion (Infrastructure Cloud Security) NON-LEADER=Total skills: (currently built). Rebuild: swapped, kept, new (marketplace-first). ·