e:** Marketplace skills vendor-tool specific (Purview). Adopt analysis methodology. Add custom overlay tool-agnostic DLP policy framework. · h3:5.4 breach-notification (NOT BUILT)=**Current status:** built **Recommended:** Custom **Marketplace candidates found:** None. Regulatory clock management (GDPR 72h, breach notification obligations jurisdiction) covered any standalone marketplace skill. **Decision rationale:** Jurisdiction-specific (GDPR 72h, PIPEDA, CCPA, sectoral regs). Operator supply applicable jurisdictions notification contacts config. Coordinates cortex (detection notification trigger) future Legal.